title: #92Noon! Rule Changes are Boring
description: Show kicks off with the Wild's L from last night, Panthers voice Mick Mixon allows us to snoop on Carolina's draft outlook, Micheletti in studio on Wild/College hockey, Twins about to lift off, and Kevin Seifert joins from the NFL Owners meetings.
